title: Kirsty Cooper
text: i am just blown away by the quality! if you think they look great on your screen, they look better in person! i had to order some more as family members wanted spares to keep. definately got that "WOW" factor from both of us and out guests! will definately be shopping here again for whatever comes my way! better than the other places out there.
